   install Docker:
===================
apt update
apt-get install     apt-transport-https     ca-certificates     curl     gnupg-agent     software-properties-common
curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/debian/gpg | sudo apt-key add -
add-apt-repository    "deb [arch=amd64] https://download.docker.com/linux/debian \
(lsb_release -cs) \
table"
pt update
pt-get install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io
ervice docker status

Initialise Docker:
====================

ip add sh
docker swarm init --advertise-addr 10.128.0.14
docker service create --replicas  -p 80:80 --name web nginx
docker service ls
curl <ip/hostname>:80
docker get pods
docker ps -a
docker service ls
docker service update --image nginx:1.2 web
docker ps
docker service rollback web
docker ps
docker service ls
docker service scale web=2
docker ps
docker node ls
docker service ps web
docker service ps
docker node ps
